## 🎯 League Structure (Season 1)

```
League 1 (Navy & Gold)          League 2 (Crimson & Silver)
────────────────────────        ────────────────────────────
Premier Tier  (top ~13)         Premier Tier  (top ~13)
Development Tier (rest)         Development Tier (rest)
